title: From the Bottom to the Top (Young Dolph Interview)

description:
Today on the show we had Young Dolph call in where he spoke about fatherhood lambo giveaway, rich slave album and more. Also, after Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day to the American Spectator and Bill Baptist for their comments on Kamala Harris we opened up the phone lines to see if any of our listeners have been accused of sleeping their way to the top!
